      title_zh: "Cryo-Builder：端到端密度→模型基础模型",
      summary_en: "A single multi-modal foundation model that ingests a cryo-EM density volume and jointly outputs atomic coordinates, sequence assignment, secondary structure, and per-residue confidence — the cryo-EM analog of AlphaFold-3.",
      summary_zh: "单一多模态基础模型，输入冷冻电镜密度图，联合输出原子坐标、序列分配、二级结构和每残基置信度 —— 冷冻电镜版的 AlphaFold-3。",
      problem: `<p><strong>AlphaFold-3 (Abramson et al., Nature 2024)</strong> revolutionized sequence→structure prediction with diffusion, but cannot use cryo-EM density as primary input. <strong>ModelAngelo (Jamali et al., Nature 2024, trained on 3,715 map-model pairs)</strong> handles density→model but is a sequential pipeline (CNN → GNN → HMM search) with cascading errors and resolution-dependent performance.</p><p>The field lacks a <em>unified foundation model</em> that learns the joint distribution P(coordinates, sequence, ss, confidence | density). This matters because: (1) it eliminates error propagation; (2) enables end-to-end uncertainty quantification; (3) provides a single model that downstream tasks can fine-tune.</p>`,
      problem_zh: `<p><strong>AlphaFold-3 (Abramson 等, Nature 2024)</strong> 用扩散革命性地解决了序列→结构预测，但无法以冷冻电镜密度为主要输入。<strong>ModelAngelo (Jamali 等, Nature 2024，3,715 对训练数据)</strong> 处理密度→模型但是顺序流水线（CNN → GNN → HMM 搜索），误差累积且分辨率依赖。</p><p>该领域缺少<em>统一基础模型</em>来学习联合分布 P(坐标, 序列, 二级结构, 置信度 | 密度)。这很重要：(1) 消除误差传播；(2) 端到端不确定性量化；(3) 提供下游任务可微调的统一模型。</p>`,
      unique_advantage: `<strong>Why ONLY Plan A enables this:</strong> ModelAngelo's 3,715 pairs lack multi-task labels (only CA positions); Cryo2Struct2Data has more density but no Q-score truth or domain partitioning. Plan A is the <em>only dataset</em> providing all 8 channels (atom, aa, ss, qscore, chain, domain, interface, segment) on 11K bio-assemblies + PHENIX-validated quality tiers — the exact substrate a unified foundation model requires.`,
      unique_advantage_zh: `<strong>为什么只有 Plan A 能支撑：</strong>ModelAngelo 的 3,715 对缺多任务标签（只有 CA 位置）；Cryo2Struct2Data 密度图更多但无 Q-score 真值或结构域划分。Plan A 是<em>唯一</em>在 11K 生物组装体上提供 8 通道（原子、氨基酸、二级结构、Q-score、链、结构域、界面、segment）+ PHENIX 验证质量分档的数据集 —— 统一基础模型所需的精确基础。`,
      approach: `<p><strong>Architecture (3 stages with shared backbone):</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Backbone:</strong> 3D Swin Transformer-V3 + FlashAttention-3, processing density in 8×8×8 Å patches with relative position encoding.</li><li><strong>Stage 1 — Residue localization:</strong> Diffusion-based denoising of a "residue token map" (like AlphaFold-3's atom diffusion).</li><li><strong>Stage 2 — Sequence assignment:</strong> Non-autoregressive transformer, per-position 20-way distribution + confidence.</li><li><strong>Stage 3 — Refinement:</strong> SE(3)-equivariant GNN refines coordinates.</li></ul><p><strong>Training (4-stage curriculum):</strong> (1) 3D MAE pretraining on 11K volumes (50% mask). (2) Multi-task supervised on all 8 Plan A channels. (3) Joint sequence+structure on Gold-tier (Q≥0.65). (4) Fine-tune with Silver/Bronze using Q-score as confidence target.</p>`,
      approach_zh: `<p><strong>架构（共享主干 + 三阶段）：</strong></p><ul><li><strong>主干：</strong>3D Swin Transformer-V3 + FlashAttention-3，密度图按 8×8×8 Å patch 处理。</li><li><strong>阶段 1 — 残基定位：</strong>"残基 token 图"扩散去噪（类似 AlphaFold-3 原子扩散模块）。</li><li><strong>阶段 2 — 序列分配：</strong>非自回归 transformer，每位置 20 类分布 + 置信度。</li><li><strong>阶段 3 — 精修：</strong>SE(3)-等价 GNN 精修原子坐标。</li></ul><p><strong>训练（四阶段课程）：</strong>(1) 11K 密度图 3D MAE 预训练（50% mask）。(2) Plan A 8 通道多任务监督。(3) Gold 档（Q≥0.65）联合序列+结构训练。(4) Silver/Bronze 数据微调，Q-score 作为置信度目标。</p>`,
      key_challenges: `<p><strong>挑战 1 — 计算成本：</strong>需 4×8 H100 集群 + 4-6 周训练。<strong>攻克：</strong>采用 patch-level masking（不是 voxel-level），降低 75% 内存；mixed precision + activation checkpointing；分阶段冻结-解冻。</p><p><strong>挑战 2 — 非自回归序列生成不稳定：</strong><strong>攻克：</strong>(a) ESM-2 预训练 token 表示初始化；(b) iterative refinement（类似 AF-3）；(c) HMM 搜索作为后处理。</p><p><strong>挑战 3 — 评估复杂性：</strong>4 任务联合评估。<strong>攻克：</strong>设计 composite score（CA RMSD + 序列一致性 + completeness + Q-score 相关性），在 CASP15-cryoEM 子集与 ModelAngelo head-to-head。</p>`,
      key_challenges_zh: `<p><strong>挑战 1 — 计算成本：</strong>需 4×8 H100 + 4-6 周。<strong>攻克：</strong>patch-level masking 降低 75% 内存；混合精度 + activation checkpointing；分阶段冻结-解冻。</p><p><strong>挑战 2 — 非自回归序列生成不稳定：</strong><strong>攻克：</strong>(a) ESM-2 预训练 token 初始化；(b) iterative refinement；(c) HMM 搜索作为后处理。</p><p><strong>挑战 3 — 评估复杂：</strong><strong>攻克：</strong>composite score（CA RMSD + 序列一致性 + completeness + Q-score 相关性）在 CASP15-cryoEM 子集 head-to-head。</p>`,
      evaluation: `<ul><li><strong>Benchmark:</strong> EMDB 2024-2025 新发布 200 条目（zero-shot）, 全分辨率分档报告</li><li><strong>主指标:</strong> CA RMSD, completeness, sequence identity, TM-score, joint accuracy</li><li><strong>对比:</strong> ModelAngelo, MICA (2025), DeepMainmast, DeepTracer, AlphaFold-3 (序列空间 upper bound)</li><li><strong>消融:</strong> 每阶段贡献 + 各通道监督贡献</li></ul>`,
      evaluation_zh: `<ul><li><strong>Benchmark:</strong> EMDB 2024-2025 新发布 200 条目（零样本），全分辨率分档</li><li><strong>主指标:</strong> CA RMSD、completeness、序列一致性、TM-score、联合准确率</li><li><strong>对比:</strong> ModelAngelo、MICA (2025)、DeepMainmast、DeepTracer、AlphaFold-3（序列空间上限）</li><li><strong>消融:</strong> 每阶段贡献 + 各通道监督贡献</li></ul>`,
      publication: `<p>🎯 <strong>Target: Nature / Nature Methods</strong>。AlphaFold-3 在 Nature 2024；ModelAngelo 在 Nature 2024。统一冷冻电镜密度基础模型对标 AF-3 在序列空间的地位，是 Nature 主刊候选。备选：Nature Methods。<br><strong>团队：</strong>1 PI + 2-3 博士生 + 1 工程师。<strong>时间线：</strong>12-18 个月端到端，子项目可阶段性发表。</p>`,
      publication_zh: `<p>🎯 <strong>目标：Nature / Nature Methods</strong>。AlphaFold-3 (Nature 2024)、ModelAngelo (Nature 2024) 是先例。统一冷冻电镜密度基础模型对标 AF-3 在序列空间的地位，是 Nature 主刊候选。备选：Nature Methods。<br><strong>团队：</strong>1 PI + 2-3 博士生 + 1 工程师。<strong>时间线：</strong>端到端 12-18 个月，可能有子项目阶段性发表。</p>`,
